interestingcomments.content: I see no actuation data in this file sorry.Try this little app with your original DNG or JPG file. software Not that good as it doesn't recognize the actuation data of your file above sorry. Jeffrey's Exif viewer can do it though. Look for "ImageUniqueID" or "Image Unique ID" in the exif data, copy the hexadecimal number and paste it in an hexadecimal converter. Gives F54 = 3924 as Shootist said above.
